Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.95,0:00:07.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}If that couple really {\i1}were{\i0} Bourbon and Vermouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.70,0:00:10.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}If they overheard me talking with Jodie{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-sensei{\r\be10}, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.07,0:00:16.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}E-Either way, I have to meet up with Haibara and check with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.28,0:00:19.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}Damn! Why didn't I realise any sooner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.68,0:00:27.84,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Since they said that the husband had been a hostage too, that doesn't fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.52,0:00:32.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They even made such an obvious blunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.35,0:00:34.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}An obvious blunder?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.40,0:00:38.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Was that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.65,0:00:39.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A trap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.30,0:00:45.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have I felt {\i1}their{\i0} presence lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:46.97,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.97,0:00:50.11,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You said they had a certain smell or something, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:54.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't felt anything, though I haven't been watching out for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.32,0:00:57.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}did{\i0} say that they believe I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:00.95,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I-Is that so? That's good then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:05.00,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What is it? Don't tell me they found out that I'm still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.44,0:01:08.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I was just checking! That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.36,0:01:10.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for calling so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.68,0:01:15.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've got to stay calm, stop panicking...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.54,0:01:36.30,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Only the light of deductions can tear apart\Nthe pitch-black shadows and bottomless darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.30,0:01:39.97,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ran collapses while investigating\Nwith Sera. Just what happened here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.97,0:01:41.70,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:43.52,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:46.19,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:13.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.98,0:03:18.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:20.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.75,0:03:22.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't "what" me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:24.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You haven't stopped glancing around since we got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:26.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone suspicious here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:28.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.72,0:03:30.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:31.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.68,0:03:34.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:37.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ever since that happened, I feel like I'm being watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:44.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've told Jodie{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-sensei{\r\be10} that that couple may have been from the Black Organisation just in case...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:50.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But if they, by any chance, noticed {\i1}that{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.05,0:03:54.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Gotta calm down. It'll be fine. I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:02.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you feeling well, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}? You're drenched with sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.35,0:04:10.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know we were going to have lunch at a Chinese restaurant with my mum after this, but would you rather go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.76,0:04:13.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'm fine! I was just thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.07,0:04:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:19.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were given some pretty hard homework, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:24.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A shutter sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:33.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I wasn't imagining it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.45,0:04:36.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I {\i1}am{\i0} being watched by someone after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:39.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But who? And why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:43.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Again! And closer than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:46.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Where? Where are they being taken from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:52.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys! What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:55.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You too, Sera{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:58.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm here for work!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:05:02.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know how there's a girl called Keiko Kitao over in Class A?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:04.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:08.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her older sister hired me for a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:12.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See that girl sitting over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:16.60,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Rumi Kitao (21)\NUniversity Student
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:16.22,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That's Rumi Kitao{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, a third-year university student.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:21.77,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And the guy sitting next to her is Ken'ya Settsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, a fourth-year university student.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:22.86,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Ken'ya Settsu (22)\NUniversity Student
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:26.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those two have been dating for half a year now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.65,0:05:33.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wants to introduce him to her parents as a possible husband, but rumour has it that he's a playboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what's more, she suspects that he hasn't cut ties with his ex-girlfriend yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.43,0:05:41.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I'm investigating him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:44.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So basically, an adultery investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.21,0:05:46.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And? How is it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:49.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right now, he's in the grey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:54.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apparently he's still got a spare key to his ex-girlfriend's flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:57.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this is the block of flats\Nwhere his ex-girlfriend lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:06:01.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you should be telling us all that, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problem! You guys know how to keep a secret, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:09.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what are you guys doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:12.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect to see you in Kanagawa prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.32,0:06:17.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mum's working for one of the residents here and is meeting with him right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:20.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're going to have lunch together after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's my mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.85,0:06:28.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You're kidding! You can't leave?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:31.80,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But we're starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:35.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. This meeting's going to take a while yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:41.82,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If you're hungry, why don't you have a little snack with Conan{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-kun{\r\be10}, and we'll meet in the lobby here tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.82,0:06:42.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:47.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess we better get some rice balls or something nearby...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:50.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, how about having those two treat you to lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:55.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were planning to have lunch together with his ex-girlfriend today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:06:58.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop joking around! I've never even seen them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:01.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an undercover investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:03.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Undercover?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:06.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do it for Keiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} from Class A!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:11.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're kidding, right? Your sister isn't coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:17.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That restaurant is pretty famous, it wasn't easy to get a reservation for all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:22.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like she has much of a choice! She said something suddenly came up with her friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:26.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it? Don't tell me you're aiming for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:30.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That ain't it! I just figured if your sister was there, she might be able to calm the air a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:35.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanna make peace with Waka at lunch today, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:38.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We haven't spoken to each other\Nsince we broke up, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.51,0:07:44.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true. Well, Kaga{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} will probably liven things up when he arrives!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:45.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:49.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you be Kei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s sister, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:50.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:57.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Ran Mouri. I was in her class last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:08:02.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She showed me your picture a few times, so I figured you might be her sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:03.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:06.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:14.23,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Actually, the plan was that I'd join them for lunch in Keiko{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-kun{\r\be10}'s place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:21.61,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If that man really {\i1}is{\i0} a playboy like the rumours suggest, he'd probably make eyes at me when she isn't looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.61,0:08:27.65,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But since you're cuter and more stylish than me, how about you take my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.67,0:08:34.55,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If he's really that kind of guy, I think he'll definitely bite if we toss him some bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:37.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Okay then. First, I need to casually put out some bait...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:43.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:52.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said you were hungry, C-Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, but we haven't decided what to eat, have we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:53.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:55.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Casual as a fish out of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:58.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then how about you eat with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.34,0:09:02.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I doubt they'll mind us bringing a kid with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:05.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.88,0:09:08.06,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well, that didn't take much bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:10.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:16.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Waka sure is late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:18.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's already past noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:19.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:24.87,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,She was out drinking until 5 this morning, so she's probably still fast asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:24.87,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Mitsuaki Kaga (22)\NUniversity Student
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:27.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There you are, Kaga!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:30.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there a toilet in this lobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:32.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just past the lift.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:35.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'll be back in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:38.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll go check on Waka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're going to see Waka,\Ncan you give her back this spare key?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't need it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:50.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ken'ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.14,0:09:56.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't drop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:01.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Now he'll be alone with Ran{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:04.16,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If he's going to give himself away, it'll be now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but would you guys mind going with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:15.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Waka hasn't sobered up yet, she might lay into her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:17.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}did{\i0} steal her boyfriend, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:26.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If there's a stranger around, Waka might be calmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:29.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.27,0:10:31.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then please come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:32.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get the feeling she might've suddenly decided she doesn't want to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:47.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, please tell her that I'd like to meet her face-to-face in order to apologise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:54.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's better than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:01.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's not answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:04.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she is asleep after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.19,0:11:08.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's use this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:11.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Waka?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:13.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:19.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, it's my phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:22.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but could you go ahead and wake Waka?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:33.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When she comes home drunk, Waka ends up sleeping in weird places.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:36.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So check in her wardrobe and stuff as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.85,0:11:37.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:40.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for making you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:42.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:45.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go out on the balcony...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:49.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Waka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}? Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:52.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Waka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:54.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Waka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:58.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is weird. She's nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:06.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.32,0:12:10.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a friend of Rumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:13.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was asked to come and get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:17.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Waka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.02,0:12:24.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Waka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:29.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on! Waka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! Waka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:30.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Waka...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:45.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:47.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:51.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}! Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:53.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:56.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Great, you're awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:12:57.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:12:59.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:00.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sera{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:07.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You collapsed in the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's terrible! I found Waka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} collapsed and bleeding in the shower!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.24,0:13:15.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. See in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:20.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police are already here and investigating right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:22.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:26.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard the shower running from out here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:30.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and when I went in, Waka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was lying on the floor, surrounded by steam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:34.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to wake her up, but\NI suddenly started feeling faint.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:36.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see anyone suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.76,0:13:38.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:41.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I searched the wardrobe and everything, but there was nobody here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:43.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you check her wardrobe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:48.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Waka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} has the habit of sleeping in weird places when she comes home drunk,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.17,0:13:50.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,according to Rumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who came with me to get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:53.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Speaking of which, where is Rumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.99,0:13:55.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:59.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for getting you involved in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:00.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:07.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found you and Waka lying in the bathroom, but I ended up passing out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:10.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I didn't see the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:15.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And since we never came back,\Nthese two came after us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:22.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'd waited 30 minutes for you,\Nand you weren't answering your mobile phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:26.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We explained the situation to the block's manager, and had him open the door for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:27.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.81,0:14:28.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:32.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we found the three of them lying in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:34.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And quickly called the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:38.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I wonder what the hell was that smell was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.51,0:14:40.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It made me kind of dizzy when I went into the shower room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:42.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's chloroform.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:52.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a form of anaesthetic —\hif you breathe in a lot of it, you lose consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:54.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In some cases, you might even die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:58.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was turned to gas and this room was filled with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:06.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, this kid turned on the ventilating fan right away, so it's fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Waka was killed by this anaesthetic?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:12.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on now, can't you tell just by looking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.38,0:15:15.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was beaten to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone beat her head in with a blunt weapon and killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.38,0:15:23.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then why did they use an anaesthetic?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And is it really Waka that died?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:28.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't see her face through that mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:31.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, let's take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:37.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Waka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.17,0:15:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't come in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:45.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, this is a strange corpse. She's winking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.22,0:15:50.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And something's trickling out of the corner of her eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:53.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Mascara?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:16:02.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}At first glance, it seems that Waka{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} was about to take a bath, when she was hit from behind and killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:05.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But could this be something else...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:16.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, according to your collective statements, the four of you had planned to have lunch together today,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:21.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and had agreed to meet here, in the lobby of the block of flats where the victim lives, shortly after noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:29.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But because the victim wasn't coming down, Rumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who also happened to be present,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:31.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,went to the victim's flat to check up on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.93,0:16:34.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And since she didn't answer when you rang the bell,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:41.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you used the spare key Settsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who used to go out with the victim, had given you to open the door and entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:50.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then Rumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} received a call from Settsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had to search for the victim on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She found the victim lying in the bathroom, but passed out due to the chloroform.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:59.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} came in afterward, and fell asleep too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:06.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And 30 minutes later, the two of you headed up here because you were concerned that the girls hadn't come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.28,0:17:09.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,where you found the three of them lying in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:12.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:20.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The safety lock was on and it took some time to get it open, so it took some time to notify you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:25.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'm a bit paranoid, so I tend to lock doors straight after coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:31.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, is it true that the victim was drinking until 5 this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:35.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was drinking with her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:38.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We also invited Settsu and Rumi, but they didn't want to come since we were going to meet today anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:42.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had to listen to her badmouthing her ex-boyfriend Settsu quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:45.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right until she fell asleep dead drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:48.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then how did the door get locked?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:53.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Of course, when I left, I woke Waka up and made her lock the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:18:00.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, this is quite an amazing flat\Nfor someone living on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:03.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Waka's father is a top executive of a famous company.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:11.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only person I've seen not be surprised by this flat was a first-year girl who joined our circle this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.46,0:18:16.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It turned out she was the daughter of the chairman of the whole business group.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:16.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:24.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you and Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r} entered this flat with the spare key, you received a call from Settsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:26.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was the call about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He asked me to look for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:33.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He left something here when he was still going out with Waka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:36.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he asked me to look for it and bring it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:40.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, he'd already asked me to find it, so I was going to look for it even if he hadn't called.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:43.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you forget here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.88,0:18:46.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A wristwatch I really liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.45,0:18:51.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it was probably still lying around somewhere in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:58.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that if Waka happened to still be asleep, I could ask her to enter with the spare key and secretly get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:03.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since she couldn't find it, Waka might have found it and thrown it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:08.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The living room is that big room connected to the balcony, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.53,0:19:09.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.24,0:19:15.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I got the call I went out to the balcony, so it was the best time to search for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:20.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a tower block, so the reception is pretty bad everywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:23.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I asked you to search for Waka, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.96,0:19:25.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:32.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Which means Rumi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} went left from the entrance into the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.66,0:19:36.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And Ran searched the right side where the bedroom is located.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of the balcony, Waka fell asleep there once when she came home drunk, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:45.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I heard about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.05,0:19:52.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She called me in a drunk daze and said\N'Feeling the wind sobers me up',
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:54.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but ended up falling asleep during the phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.26,0:19:59.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I came here because I was worried, she was leaning against the balcony, fast asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:02.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She also slept under the bed once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:08.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this time, she didn't sleep on the balcony or under the bed, but in the shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.94,0:20:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At eternal rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:18.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the person who did that to her is someone who had a key to this flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:21.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:22.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:28.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her ex-boyfriend Settsu had a spare key, but I didn't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:31.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe you made the victim drink until she blacked out
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.72,0:20:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and sneakily took the key with you when you left?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:38.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then when you came here earlier, you could have just tossed it somewhere to deceive us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.64,0:20:43.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or you could've just stayed up here until the meeting time just after midday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.78,0:20:46.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Rumi might have a key too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:51.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was sharing the flat with Waka until Settsu and Waka started dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.46,0:20:53.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I returned that key a long time ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:54.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:06.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If all three of them might have had a key, that means all three could have performed the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:07.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only ones who could have killed Waka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} before Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} found her are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:17.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Settsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Kaga{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. I doubt it could've been anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.14,0:21:19.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:26.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaga{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} only arrived shortly before Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and Rumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} went to Waka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s flat to check on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:32.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And about 30 minutes earlier, Settsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} went to the toilet for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.03,0:21:40.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they had a key to Waka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s flat and took the stairs, where no security cameras are installed,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.99,0:21:44.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they could have killed Waka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} without being seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.91,0:21:49.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In contrast, Rumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was with me the whole time until she came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.63,0:21:55.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And since she didn't even go to the toilet before she went to Waka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s flat,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.98,0:21:57.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the crime would have been impossible for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.45,0:21:59.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were with Rumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.25,0:22:01.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or rather —\hwho the heck are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.32,0:22:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.02,0:22:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was hired by Rumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:36.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.84,0:23:42.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.97,0:23:44.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for picking them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.40,0:23:46.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.48,0:23:48.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful not to drop them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.65,0:23:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if that corpse wasn't Waka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, then it's a different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.69,0:23:58.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.16,0:24:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the next Conan: The Bathroom Where Ran Blacks Out (Part II)!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.17,0:24:09.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Wink!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.13,0:24:10.39,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's nearly June!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.39,0:24:11.30,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,May streams by in the blink of an eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.30,0:24:14.12,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Mascara's streaming out of your eye!
